{"tid":1203134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"家庭遠足野餐必備2大神器！！！","createTime":"2019-06-11T11:36:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T12:02:54.000Z","uid":6435,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7dd4a834ed19b9d49bb1f0d464c1a967507a1f22","tid":1203134,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:36:58.000Z","msg":"去遠足野餐必備第一樣野梗係GIP啦<br />\n大大個GIP裝野裝得多 又夠硬淨<br />\n你諗下平時去旅行 機場運行李班友掉黎掉去都唔爛你就知好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SmnirmP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSmnirmP.jpg&h=a7473785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nCPPfqdr3x8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnCPPfqdr3x8&d=%2FodnS2mEGvHoUZPzyf%2FmNXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=43e742ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nCPPfqdr3x8</a><br />\n<br />\n口渴果陣飲咩好？ 梗係飲雀巢咖啡<br />\n連警察都讚好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得要飲呢隻 原汁原味最正宗<br />\n<img src=\"http://viso.com.hk/image/cache/data/00.product/Nescafe/Regular-600x600_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fviso.com.hk%2Fimage%2Fcache%2Fdata%2F00.product%2FNescafe%2FRegular-600x600_0.jpg&h=68e58f86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者你中意飲其他味都得<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nestle.com.hk/brands/Coffee/CanCoffee/PublishingImages/NESCAFE%20CAN%20group%20shot%205_24.4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nestle.com.hk%2Fbrands%2FCoffee%2FCanCoffee%2FPublishingImages%2FNESCAFE%2520CAN%2520group%2520shot%25205_24.4.jpg&h=6bda5986&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nc3i1DEj1eM?t=243\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fnc3i1DEj1eM%3Ft%3D243&d=%2FodnS2mEGvHoUZPzyf%2FmNXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=f0f622e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nc3i1DEj1eM?t=243</a>"},{"pid":"79a4a09b05e2cf5ba7815953a3c764344dd3cf73","tid":1203134,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0beedf62e29b7437ecbbf19480e313d2abc7d9bc","tid":1203134,"uid":4550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:41:35.000Z","msg":"我好鍾意飲咖啡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c70969cb0a023a96a6dc6636f828f87f778bace","tid":1203134,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:44:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c35f4057dd422d48344125592d4833e1856f44d","tid":1203134,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:47:52.000Z","msg":"用羊毛襪應該夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日天氣一定好凍 大家著羊毛襪出去保暖"},{"pid":"679ba298ab3d499ee0e6482f13ac95a681cd253b","tid":1203134,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:48:44.000Z","msg":"SORRY<br />\n貼錯LINK<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我其實想介紹返呢個靚GIP<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vagcbcfHiaw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvagcbcfHiaw&d=%2FodnS2mEGvHoUZPzyf%2FmNXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=ece63ebf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vagcbcfHiaw</a><br />\n<br />\n同埋推介下我最鐘意飲既雀巢咖啡<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XrihkdKKduA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXrihkdKKduA&d=%2FodnS2mEGvHoUZPzyf%2FmNXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=992bfe15\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XrihkdKKduA</a>"},{"pid":"3db79c98e7685ece9a5a3d8c0dfb912b77f5af6e","tid":1203134,"uid":60456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0